lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Richard Gasquet beat unseeded Argentine Diego Schwartzman 7-6 (4), 6-1 to win the European Open final on Sunday and clinch a 14th career title.

headline.print_headline: Gasquet Beats Schwartzman to Win European Open Final
